## 2️⃣ Parallel CI Analysis

The pipeline executes the following stages **in parallel**:

### 🔹 a) Code Stability Check
- Run unit tests, verify build integrity
- Failures halt the pipeline if not skipped

### 🔹 b) Code Quality Analysis
- Run static code analysis tools (Checkstyle, PMD)
- Generate quality reports

### 🔹 c) Code Coverage Analysis
- Run tests with coverage tool (JaCoCo / Cobertura)
- Produce coverage reports in Jenkins

